                     <interp inst="t18310407-61-off347" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310407-61-off347" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18310407-61-cd348" type="crimeDate">27th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310407-61-off347 t18310407-61-cd348"></join>, 2 saws, value 11s.; 4 planes, value 12s.; 1 oil-stone, value 4s.; 2 hammers, value 2s.; 15 chisels, value 5s.; 1 pair of compasses, value 1s.; 1 square, value 1s. 6d.; 1 pair of pincers, value 1s.; 4 gimblets, value 9d.; 2 files, value 9d. and 1 tool-basket, value 1s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18310407-61-victim581" type="victimName">
                     Matthew 
                     Headen
                  <interp inst="t18310407-61-victim581" type="surname" value="Headen"></interp>
